67 Part 3 of Article 7 of Chapter 3 of Title 20 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
68 relating to the Georgia Student Finance Authority, is amended in Subpart 7, relating to grants
69 to children of law enforcement officers, firefighters, and prison guards, by revising Code
70 Section 20-3-450, relating to legislative findings and purpose of subpart, as follows:
71 "20-3-450.
72 The General Assembly finds that certain citizens are called upon to enforce the criminal
73 laws of this state and to protect persons and properties within the state and that they
74 provide a valuable and vital public service to the state and to citizens and properties within
75 the state at a great personal sacrifice and risk to their own lives and well-being. The
76 purpose of the General Assembly, as provided for in this subpart, is to enable the authority
77 to provide educational grant assistance to the children and spouses of such persons who are
78 killed or permanently disabled in the line of duty."
